load ../skills-never-grant.maude

--- Coverage: profile caps flow into the effective authority (skill present, no effect).
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SKILLS-NEVER-GRANT :
  profile(read ; bash) skillTools(mt) effective(mt)
  =>! profile(mt) skillTools(mt) effective(read ; bash) .

--- Coverage: a skill's allowed-tools are consumed as provenance (never granted).
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SKILLS-NEVER-GRANT :
  skillTools(write)
  =>! skillTools(mt) .

--- Bite: a tool a skill lists but the profile does not permit never enters the
--- effective authority. The RESIDUAL soup var means `write` in ANY reachable
--- effective set is a solution, so No solution proves the skill cannot widen.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SKILLS-NEVER-GRANT :
  profile(read) skillTools(write) effective(mt)
  =>* effective(write ; E:CapSet) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: with an empty profile a skill grants nothing, whatever it lists.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SKILLS-NEVER-GRANT :
  profile(mt) skillTools(read ; write) effective(mt)
  =>* effective(C:Cap ; E:CapSet) RESIDUAL:Cfg .
